params.description: Required. The list of file annotation requests. Right now we support only one AnnotateFileRequest in BatchAnnotateFilesRequest.

params.description: Optional. Target project and location to make a call. Format: projects/{project-id}/locations/{location-id}. If no parent is specified, a region will be chosen automatically.
